    "docs/frontend-api.md:list:3f9987fd6d5763471a809790928e57f06d01a80598abab313dad9434565dcb35": {
      "kind": "list",
      "source": "__ELBOT_CODE_0__ — 鉴权失败，连接关闭",
      "source_file": "docs/frontend-api.md",
      "source_hash": "3f9987fd6d5763471a809790928e57f06d01a80598abab313dad9434565dcb35",
      "translation": "__ELBOT_CODE_0__ — Authentication failed, connection closed",
      "updated_at": 1782901460
    },
    "docs/frontend-api.md:list:b0c6a317c8bff1f97521ff2e8643e9417924fd3e72ec2525d37052533e8277e3": {
      "kind": "list",
      "source": "__ELBOT_CODE_0__ — 鉴权通过，可以开始交互",
      "source_file": "docs/frontend-api.md",
      "source_hash": "b0c6a317c8bff1f97521ff2e8643e9417924fd3e72ec2525d37052533e8277e3",
      "translation": "__ELBOT_CODE_0__ — Authentication successful, interaction can begin",
      "updated_at": 1782901460
    },
    "docs/frontend-api.md:paragraph:07b5913353f1cfc85c936e91f62ef2c8f31d27746f18fd6f2f65d549eb9ce9f0": {
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "source": "LLM 流式输出的一段增量文本。前端应追加到当前正在生成的消息末尾。\n",
      "source_file": "docs/frontend-api.md",
      "source_hash": "07b5913353f1cfc85c936e91f62ef2c8f31d27746f18fd6f2f65d549eb9ce9f0",
      "translation": "An incremental piece of text streamed from the LLM. The frontend should append it to the end of the message currently being generated.\n",
      "updated_at": 1782901460
    },
    "docs/frontend-api.md:paragraph:08d5a3fcb505c98f34ecf262f0eb651b41628e3f9e32169f9165e4a3750863be": {
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "source": "将文本作为用户输入交给 Agent 处理。服务端不回复确认，处理结果通过 chat/stream 等消息异步返回。\n",
      "source_file": "docs/frontend-api.md",
      "source_hash": "08d5a3fcb505c98f34ecf262f0eb651b41628e3f9e32169f9165e4a3750863be",
      "translation": "Pass text as user input to the Agent for processing. The server does not send a confirmation response; processing results are returned asynchronously via messages such as chat/stream.\n",
      "updated_at": 1782901460
    },
    "docs/frontend-api.md:paragraph:0bdc1a60c897acb886618f6c49aed63731d852925f2dca2d08709c28afbac594": {
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "source": "处理过程中发生的错误。\n",
      "source_file": "docs/frontend-api.md",
      "source_hash": "0bdc1a60c897acb886618f6c49aed63731d852925f2dca2d08709c28afbac594",
      "translation": "An error that occurred during processing.\n",
      "updated_at": 1782901460
    },
    "docs/frontend-api.md:paragraph:20595b74e8d8c160a3282602b9e0f1b7519133fd993639fb2c017a01f1d9f0a3": {
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "source": "支持推理输出的模型在生成过程中推送的推理文本。前端可选择展示或隐藏。\n",
      "source_file": "docs/frontend-api.md",
      "source_hash": "20595b74e8d8c160a3282602b9e0f1b7519133fd993639fb2c017a01f1d9f0a3",
      "translation": "Reasoning text pushed by models that support reasoning output during the generation process. The frontend can choose to display or hide it.\n",
      "updated_at": 1782901460
    },
    "docs/frontend-api.md:paragraph:2e286a691b516cf7a4f664ce6a819ae7ddece62d6dc8f2cb561ee3ab85d979c1": {
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "source": "在 __ELBOT_CODE_0__ 的 __ELBOT_CODE_1__ 中配置：\n",
      "source_file": "docs/frontend-api.md",
      "source_hash": "2e286a691b516cf7a4f664ce6a819ae7ddece62d6dc8f2cb561ee3ab85d979c1",
      "translation": "Configure in __ELBOT_CODE_1__ of __ELBOT_CODE_0__:\n",
      "updated_at": 1782901460
    },
    "docs/frontend-api.md:paragraph:2fc0902aa8673a668728cfd1db0c298a7d033d44a676a2e16043765275aeb295": {
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "source": "Token 在 __ELBOT_CODE_0__ 中按 client_id 映射到环境变量名，服务端从对应环境变量读取实际值。\n",
      "source_file": "docs/frontend-api.md",
      "source_hash": "2fc0902aa8673a668728cfd1db0c298a7d033d44a676a2e16043765275aeb295",
      "translation": "Tokens are mapped to environment variable names by client_id in __ELBOT_CODE_0__, and the server reads the actual values from the corresponding environment variables.\n",
      "updated_at": 1782901460
    },
    "docs/frontend-api.md:paragraph:3dca443f29bdee748af053d019fd57f759fb7b0401673261d850673661493415": {
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "source": "服务端校验 token 后回复：\n",
      "source_file": "docs/frontend-api.md",
      "source_hash": "3dca443f29bdee748af053d019fd57f759fb7b0401673261d850673661493415",
      "translation": "The server will respond after validating the token:\n",
      "updated_at": 1782901460
    },
    "docs/frontend-api.md:paragraph:4e842da1ad9d6f0bbe875b1adb0c6fad1a7b86929891dd28bb6798bc67d0c36e": {
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "source": "ElBot 前后端分离，CLI 远程协议是基于 WebSocket 的 JSON 消息协议。",
      "source_file": "docs/frontend-api.md",
      "source_hash": "4e842da1ad9d6f0bbe875b1adb0c6fad1a7b86929891dd28bb6798bc67d0c36e",
      "translation": "ElBot uses a decoupled frontend and backend; the CLI remote protocol is a JSON messaging protocol based on WebSocket.",
      "updated_at": 1782901460
    },
    "docs/frontend-api.md:paragraph:5a6db705fd1ed0883cbccd006faa75c3bb039679fcf08f1c145582eba34308ee": {
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "source": "补全候选列表，__ELBOT_CODE_0__ 对应请求时的 __ELBOT_CODE_1__。__ELBOT_CODE_2__/__ELBOT_CODE_3__ 指示应替换原输入文本的字节区间。\n",
      "source_file": "docs/frontend-api.md",
      "source_hash": "5a6db705fd1ed0883cbccd006faa75c3bb039679fcf08f1c145582eba34308ee",
      "translation": "Completion candidate list, where __ELBOT_CODE_0__ corresponds to __ELBOT_CODE_1__ at the time of the request. __ELBOT_CODE_2__/__ELBOT_CODE_3__ indicates the byte range of the original input text to be replaced.\n",
      "updated_at": 1782901460
    },
    "docs/frontend-api.md:paragraph:5ef8927fcc5d9ac94297051b2c239164249298fd75c4acb64ed10db7d30fe6d8": {
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "source": "服务端按顺序尝试从这些环境变量读取 token 值，与客户端发送的 token 比对。",
      "source_file": "docs/frontend-api.md",
      "source_hash": "5ef8927fcc5d9ac94297051b2c239164249298fd75c4acb64ed10db7d30fe6d8",
      "translation": "The server attempts to read token values from these environment variables in order and compares them with the token sent by the client.",
      "updated_at": 1782901460
    },
    "docs/frontend-api.md:paragraph:6207569319205d9e1e4bc253dbd578cd7a489bcb074bc59ae11dc488cdeaca8e": {
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "source": "服务端回复 __ELBOT_CODE_0__。\n",
      "source_file": "docs/frontend-api.md",
      "source_hash": "6207569319205d9e1e4bc253dbd578cd7a489bcb074bc59ae11dc488cdeaca8e",
      "translation": "The server responds with __ELBOT_CODE_0__.\n",
      "updated_at": 1782901460
    },
    "docs/frontend-api.md:paragraph:65871e3751ccda89ce7660fd203231fc57211d7a09301110b7304d272c4ca548": {
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "source": "默认地址 __ELBOT_CODE_0__。地址和端口在 __ELBOT_CODE_1__ 配置中修改。\n",
      "source_file": "docs/frontend-api.md",
      "source_hash": "65871e3751ccda89ce7660fd203231fc57211d7a09301110b7304d272c4ca548",
      "translation": "Default address __ELBOT_CODE_0__. The address and port can be modified in the __ELBOT_CODE_1__ configuration.\n",
      "updated_at": 1782901460
    },
    "docs/frontend-api.md:paragraph:7eed2959946534c06d7d21426b2f96e69b3f122ae04870bbb4981c8bfe21d403": {
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "source": "运行状态快照，前端可用于状态栏展示。__ELBOT_CODE_0__ 取值：\n",
      "source_file": "docs/frontend-api.md",
      "source_hash": "7eed2959946534c06d7d21426b2f96e69b3f122ae04870bbb4981c8bfe21d403",
      "translation": "A snapshot of the runtime status, which the frontend can use for status bar display. Possible values for __ELBOT_CODE_0__: \n",
      "updated_at": 1782901460
    },
    "docs/frontend-api.md:paragraph:9c8eb32c21d9df0b438fd23ffb2e38cc9a5fab3b0de47fa559d3e88da34aee1f": {
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "source": "标记当前流式消息已结束，前端可以固定该消息。\n",
      "source_file": "docs/frontend-api.md",
      "source_hash": "9c8eb32c21d9df0b438fd23ffb2e38cc9a5fab3b0de47fa559d3e88da34aee1f",
      "translation": "Marks that the current streaming message has ended; the frontend can now pin this message.\n",
      "updated_at": 1782901460
    },
    "docs/frontend-api.md:paragraph:adc6e62a5f040ab39ae50af75b7795b801bf8cbee04bfa0f9d5b608f190bfbe6": {
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "source": "非对话场景的通知消息，如 Cron 结果、Hook 输出、Elnis 事件报告等。\n",
      "source_file": "docs/frontend-api.md",
      "source_hash": "adc6e62a5f040ab39ae50af75b7795b801bf8cbee04bfa0f9d5b608f190bfbe6",
      "translation": "Notification messages for non-dialogue scenarios, such as Cron results, Hook output, Elnis event reports, etc.\n",
      "updated_at": 1782901460
    },
    "docs/frontend-api.md:paragraph:b7ec5aa79f7feac3899c5678ac8ae25ffaad189f22324caf4c4cfccea1c39825": {
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "source": "Agent 完成处理后发送的完整回复消息。\n",
      "source_file": "docs/frontend-api.md",
      "source_hash": "b7ec5aa79f7feac3899c5678ac8ae25ffaad189f22324caf4c4cfccea1c39825",
      "translation": "The complete reply message sent after the Agent finishes processing.\n",
      "updated_at": 1782901460
    },
    "docs/frontend-api.md:paragraph:beddd3b0cb61ba1e2276cc7b9e8194ab03806e92e68e795fe0a9123f9de9d06c": {
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "source": "连接建立后，客户端必须立即发送一条 __ELBOT_CODE_0__ 消息：\n",
      "source_file": "docs/frontend-api.md",
      "source_hash": "beddd3b0cb61ba1e2276cc7b9e8194ab03806e92e68e795fe0a9123f9de9d06c",
      "translation": "After the connection is established, the client must immediately send a __ELBOT_CODE_0__ message:\n",
      "updated_at": 1782901460
    },
    "docs/frontend-api.md:paragraph:c8861d11db55e8e2431a168019b157e859cf13ebee7ebcb34a2aef657aad39f1": {
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "source": "任何能连 WebSocket 的客户端都可以作为 ElBot 前端——TUI、Web、移动端、甚至另一台机器上的脚本。\n",
      "source_file": "docs/frontend-api.md",
      "source_hash": "c8861d11db55e8e2431a168019b157e859cf13ebee7ebcb34a2aef657aad39f1",
      "translation": "Any client capable of connecting to a WebSocket can serve as an ElBot frontend—TUI, Web, mobile, or even a script on another machine.\n",
      "updated_at": 1782901460
    },
    "docs/frontend-api.md:paragraph:d1abaeddc044b99ba2fc6cb16a5f4a9de092704d243ed70e7fdf2ae42b7dcabd": {
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "source": "__ELBOT_CODE_0__ 是 client_id 到环境变量名列表的映射。",
      "source_file": "docs/frontend-api.md",
      "source_hash": "d1abaeddc044b99ba2fc6cb16a5f4a9de092704d243ed70e7fdf2ae42b7dcabd",
      "translation": "__ELBOT_CODE_0__ is a mapping from client_id to a list of environment variable names.",
      "updated_at": 1782901460
    },
    "docs/frontend-api.md:paragraph:d49cedeb924838e552674bb9b1dcf7f81c505541846bef91ace96aa613baecca": {
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "source": "流式结束后，用最终完整文本替换之前累积的流式内容。可能和流式拼接的结果不同（Hook 可能修改了输出）。\n",
      "source_file": "docs/frontend-api.md",
      "source_hash": "d49cedeb924838e552674bb9b1dcf7f81c505541846bef91ace96aa613baecca",
      "translation": "After streaming ends, replace the previously accumulated streaming content with the final complete text. This may differ from the result of streaming concatenation (Hooks may have modified the output).\n",
      "updated_at": 1782901460
    },
    "docs/frontend-api.md:paragraph:ee24b5b4eaff5b66dfdc166fbea541a991b17968e5d2735a59d7b7ee0e1387c6": {
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "source": "更多前端示例见 [elbot-showcase/frontend](https://github.com/Elfreese/elbot-showcase/tree/main/frontend)。\n",
      "source_file": "docs/frontend-api.md",
      "source_hash": "ee24b5b4eaff5b66dfdc166fbea541a991b17968e5d2735a59d7b7ee0e1387c6",
      "translation": "For more frontend examples, see [elbot-showcase/frontend](https://github.com/Elfreese/elbot-showcase/tree/main/frontend).\n",
      "updated_at": 1782901460
    },
    "docs/frontend-api.md:paragraph:f8ef0da23137f3d5fa2083b4da97c426fab6d982a039be397799c18d82c3d519": {
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "source": "请求当前输入文本的命令补全候选。__ELBOT_CODE_0__ 用于匹配响应。__ELBOT_CODE_1__ 为光标在 __ELBOT_CODE_2__ 中的字节偏移，省略时取末尾。\n",
      "source_file": "docs/frontend-api.md",
      "source_hash": "f8ef0da23137f3d5fa2083b4da97c426fab6d982a039be397799c18d82c3d519",
      "translation": "Request command completion candidates for the current input text. __ELBOT_CODE_0__ is used to match the response. __ELBOT_CODE_1__ is the byte offset of the cursor in __ELBOT_CODE_2__, defaulting to the end if omitted.\n",
      "updated_at": 1782901460
    },
    "docs/frontend-api.md:paragraph:f91264031fb65d397387ea450cbf17cb02f56254b7b0fe0b70f38ea1985b11c0": {
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "source": "环境变量可从系统环境或配置目录 __ELBOT_CODE_0__ 读取。\n",
      "source_file": "docs/frontend-api.md",
      "source_hash": "f91264031fb65d397387ea450cbf17cb02f56254b7b0fe0b70f38ea1985b11c0",
      "translation": "Environment variables can be read from the system environment or the configuration directory __ELBOT_CODE_0__.\n",
      "updated_at": 1782901460
    },
    "docs/frontend-api.md:paragraph:f98e302254d6d3b6c50195bbf98f2f0801835dca84ec3d3889d88aedf42f626b": {
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "source": "所有消息均为 JSON，共享同一个结构：\n",
      "source_file": "docs/frontend-api.md",
      "source_hash": "f98e302254d6d3b6c50195bbf98f2f0801835dca84ec3d3889d88aedf42f626b",
      "translation": "All messages are in JSON and share the same structure:\n",
      "updated_at": 1782901460
    },
